  "scene1": {
    "text": "The rain falls relentlessly, drumming against the worn cobblestones of your village. Tonight marks eighteen years since your arrival in this world - a life spent without the guidance of parents, but not without care.",
    "image": "scene1.png"
  },
  "scene2": {
    "text": "For years, the old caretaker looked after you when no one else would. Teaching you, guiding you, preparing you for a world that can be both harsh and wondrous.\n\nTonight, as the rain falls outside, they've passed peacefully in their sleep. Their final words still echo in your mind:",
    "image": "scene2.png"
  },
  "final_words": {
    "text": "\"Your destiny awaits beyond these village borders. You have a hero's heart - don't let it remain hidden here.\""
  },
  "background_intros": {
    "Acolyte": {
      "text": "Their faith sustained them, even at the end. You were raised amidst prayers and rituals, guided by the old caretaker's unwavering devotion. Though they served as a humble acolyte rather than a high priest, their spiritual connection never faltered.",
      "image": "scene3.png"
    },
    "Criminal": {
      "text": "Even in their final days, they kept secrets well. The old caretaker taught you to survive in the shadows, to observe without being seen. They spoke little of their past, but their skills spoke volumes about a life lived beyond the law's reach.",
      "image": "scene3.png"
    },
    "Entertainer": {
      "text": "Their stories and songs brightened even the darkest nights. The old caretaker taught you to find beauty in performance, to create joy through melody and movement, to win hearts with words and wit. Their smile remained even when pain clouded their eyes.",
      "image": "scene3.png"
    },
    "Folk Hero": {
      "text": "They knew the wilds better than the village streets. The old caretaker taught you to read the stars, to track game, to live in harmony with nature's harsh beauty. Their tales of distant lands filled your dreams with horizons unseen.",
      "image": "scene3.png"
    },
    "Artisan": {
